hadiths[216]{hadithnumber,text}:
5646,"saiyedna Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab main Najran mein aaya, to wahan ke) nasrani ( logon ne mujh par aetraz kya ke tum padhtey ho ke) aayat ( ''aey Harun ki behan '' ( Maryam : 28 ( (yani Maryam (Alaihissalam) ko Harun ki behan kaha hai) halanke ( saiyedna Harun (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) ke bhai they aur) Musa (Alaihissalam) , Esa (Alaihissalam) se itni muddat pahley they ( phir Maryam (Alaihissalam) Harun (Alaihissalam) ki behan kyonkar ho sakti hain?) , jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (ye wo Harun thodi hain jo Musa ke bhai they) Bani-Israeel ki aadat thi (jaisey ab sab ki aadat hai) ke wo paighambaron aur agley nekon ke naam par naam rakhtey they."
5647,"saiyedna Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab main Najran mein aaya, to wahan ke) nasrani ( logon ne mujh par aetraz kya ke tum padhtey ho ke) aayat ( ''aey Harun ki behan '' ( Maryam : 28 ( (yani Maryam (Alaihissalam) ko Harun ki behan kaha hai) halanke ( saiyedna Harun (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) ke bhai they aur) Musa (Alaihissalam) , Esa (Alaihissalam) se itni muddat pahley they ( phir Maryam (Alaihissalam) Harun (Alaihissalam) ki behan kyonkar ho sakti hain?) , jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (ye wo Harun thodi hain jo Musa ke bhai they) Bani-Israeel ki aadat thi (jaisey ab sab ki aadat hai) ke wo paighambaron aur agley nekon ke naam par naam rakhtey they."
5648,"Motamir bin Sulaiman ne kaha : maine rukban se suna, wo apne walid se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein apne ghulaamon ke ye char naam rakhney se mana farmaya : Aflah ( zyada kaamyaab), Ribah (munaafe wala) , Yasar ( aasani wala (aur Naafe (nafa pahunchane-wala ( ."
5649,"Motamir bin Sulaiman ne kaha : maine rukban se suna, wo apne walid se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein apne ghulaamon ke ye char naam rakhney se mana farmaya : Aflah ( zyada kaamyaab), Ribah (munaafe wala) , Yasar ( aasani wala (aur Naafe (nafa pahunchane-wala ( ."
5650,"Jarir ne Rukein bin Rabe se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne ladkey (ghulam, khaadim) ka naam ribaah, Yasar, Aflah, aur Naafe na rakho."
5651,"Jarir ne Rukein bin Rabe se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne ladkey (ghulam, khaadim) ka naam ribaah, Yasar, Aflah, aur Naafe na rakho."
5652,"Mina saiyedna Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sabse zyada pasand Allah Taala ko char kalimey hain ( سُبْحَانَ اللهِ , وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ , وَلاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ , وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ ( inmein se jis ko chahey pahley kahey koi nuqsan na hoga aur apne ghulam ka naam Yasar, Ribah aur Najeeh (iske wahi mana hain jo Aflah ke hain) aur Aflah na rakho. isliye ke to poochhega wahan wo hai (yani Yasar ya Ribah ya najeeh ya Aflah ( wo kahega nahi hai.'' Samra ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi char naam farmaai . to zyada mat naql karna mujh se."
5653,"Mina saiyedna Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sabse zyada pasand Allah Taala ko char kalimey hain ( سُبْحَانَ اللهِ , وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ , وَلاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ , وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ ( inmein se jis ko chahey pahley kahey koi nuqsan na hoga aur apne ghulam ka naam Yasar, Ribah aur Najeeh (iske wahi mana hain jo Aflah ke hain) aur Aflah na rakho. isliye ke to poochhega wahan wo hai (yani Yasar ya Ribah ya najeeh ya Aflah ( wo kahega nahi hai.'' Samra ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi char naam farmaai . to zyada mat naql karna mujh se."
5654,"Jareer, Rooh bin-Qasim aur Shoba sab ne Mansoor se Zuhair ki sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, Jarir aur Rooh ki hadis qissey samet Zuhair ki hadis jaisi hai. aur jo Shoba ki hadis hai. usmein sirf ghulam ka naam rakhney ka zikr hai, unhon-ne char behtreen kalimaat ka zikr nahi kya."
5655,"Jareer, Rooh bin-Qasim aur Shoba sab ne Mansoor se Zuhair ki sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, Jarir aur Rooh ki hadis qissey samet Zuhair ki hadis jaisi hai. aur jo Shoba ki hadis hai. usmein sirf ghulam ka naam rakhney ka zikr hai, unhon-ne char behtreen kalimaat ka zikr nahi kya."
5656,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irada farmaya ke aap Yala ( buland ( , barkat , Aflah , Yasar Naafe jaisey naam rakhney se mana farma dein, phir maine dekha ke aap khamosh ho gaey, phir aap ki rihlat hui to aap ne un naamon se nahi roka tha, phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse rokney ka irada kya to unhon-ne bhi (ye irada) tark kar diya."
5657,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irada farmaya ke aap Yala ( buland ( , barkat , Aflah , Yasar Naafe jaisey naam rakhney se mana farma dein, phir maine dekha ke aap khamosh ho gaey, phir aap ki rihlat hui to aap ne un naamon se nahi roka tha, phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse rokney ka irada kya to unhon-ne bhi (ye irada) tark kar diya."
5658,"Ahmad-bin-Hanbal, Zuhair-bin-Harab, Muhammad-bin-Musanna, Ubaidullah bin Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Bishr ne (un sab ne) kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aasiya (nafarmani karne wali) ka naam tabdeel kar diya aur farmaya : tum jameela ( khoobsurat) ho. Ahmed ne mujhey khabar di ki jagah se riwayat hai, kaha hai."
5659,"Ahmad-bin-Hanbal, Zuhair-bin-Harab, Muhammad-bin-Musanna, Ubaidullah bin Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Bishr ne (un sab ne) kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aasiya (nafarmani karne wali) ka naam tabdeel kar diya aur farmaya : tum jameela ( khoobsurat) ho. Ahmed ne mujhey khabar di ki jagah se riwayat hai, kaha hai."
5660,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik sahibzadi ko aasiya kaha jata tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska naam jameela rakh diya."
5661,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik sahibzadi ko aasiya kaha jata tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska naam jameela rakh diya."
5662,"Amr Naqid aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hadis bayan ki. alfaz Amr ke hain. donon ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne aale-Talha ke aazad karda ghulam Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Kureb se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : (pahley Ummul-Momenin Hazrat ( Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam barra tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka naam badal kar Juweriya rakh diya. aapko pasand na tha. ke is tarah kaha jaey ke aap barra (nekiyon wali) ke yahan se nikal gaey. ibne-abi-Umar ki hadis mein hai : Kureb se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna."
5663,"Amr Naqid aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hadis bayan ki. alfaz Amr ke hain. donon ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne aale-Talha ke aazad karda ghulam Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Kureb se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : (pahley Ummul-Momenin Hazrat ( Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam barra tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka naam badal kar Juweriya rakh diya. aapko pasand na tha. ke is tarah kaha jaey ke aap barra (nekiyon wali) ke yahan se nikal gaey. ibne-abi-Umar ki hadis mein hai : Kureb se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna."
5664,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin-Bashar ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Ataa-bin-abi-Memoona se, unhon-ne abu Raafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Zenab (binte-Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) (ka naam barra tha to kaha gaya ke wo (naam batatey waqt khud) apni parsaai bayan karti hain, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka naam Zenab rakh diya. hadis ke alfaz ibne-Bashar ke ilawa baqi sab ke (bayan kiya hua) hain. ibne-Abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki."
5665,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin-Bashar ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Ataa-bin-abi-Memoona se, unhon-ne abu Raafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Zenab (binte-Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) (ka naam barra tha to kaha gaya ke wo (naam batatey waqt khud) apni parsaai bayan karti hain, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka naam Zenab rakh diya. hadis ke alfaz ibne-Bashar ke ilawa baqi sab ke (bayan kiya hua) hain. ibne-Abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki."
5666,"Waleed-bin-Kasir ne kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Ata ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Zenab binte- Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya , kaha : mera naam barra tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera naam Zenab rakh diya. unhon-ne kaha : jab Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) aap ke hibaala nikah mein dakhil huin to unka naam bhi barra tha, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka naam bhi Zenab rakha."
5667,"Waleed-bin-Kasir ne kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Ata ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Zenab binte- Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya , kaha : mera naam barra tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera naam Zenab rakh diya. unhon-ne kaha : jab Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) aap ke hibaala nikah mein dakhil huin to unka naam bhi barra tha, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka naam bhi Zenab rakha."
5668,"Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib ne Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Ata se riwayat ki, kaha : maine apni beti ka naam barra rakha to Hazrat Zenab binte-abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye naam rakhney se mana farmaya hai. aur (bataya ke) mera naam bhi pahley barra rakha gaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum log apni paarsaai na bayan karo Allah Taala hi khub janta hai ke tum mein se neku-kaar kon hai? ( ghar ke) logon ne kaha : phir ham iska kiya naam rakhein ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : iska naam Zenab rakh do."
5669,"Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib ne Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Ata se riwayat ki, kaha : maine apni beti ka naam barra rakha to Hazrat Zenab binte-abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye naam rakhney se mana farmaya hai. aur (bataya ke) mera naam bhi pahley barra rakha gaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum log apni paarsaai na bayan karo Allah Taala hi khub janta hai ke tum mein se neku-kaar kon hai? ( ghar ke) logon ne kaha : phir ham iska kiya naam rakhein ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : iska naam Zenab rakh do."
5670,"Saeed-bin-Amr-ash-ashi,  Ahmad-bin-Hanbal (Rehmatullahi-alaih) aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki. alfaz imam Ahmed ke hain, ash-ashi ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne khabar di jabke doosrey ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki. abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ke nazdeek sabse zaleel samjha jane wala naam us shakhs ka hai jo shahanshaah kahlaaey aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ne apni riwayat mein izafa kiya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke siwa koi ( badhshahat ka ( Malik nahi hai. ash-ashi ka qaul hai : Sufiyan ne kaha : jaisey ( shahanshaah ( hai. aur Ahmad-bin-Hanbal ne kaha : maine abu Amr ( Ishaq-bin-muraar Shebani , nahwi , koofi) se akhna' ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : (iske mana hain) auza' (intihai haqeer)."
5671,"Saeed-bin-Amr-ash-ashi,  Ahmad-bin-Hanbal (Rehmatullahi-alaih) aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki. alfaz imam Ahmed ke hain, ash-ashi ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne khabar di jabke doosrey ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki. abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ke nazdeek sabse zaleel samjha jane wala naam us shakhs ka hai jo shahanshaah kahlaaey aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ne apni riwayat mein izafa kiya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke siwa koi ( badhshahat ka ( Malik nahi hai. ash-ashi ka qaul hai : Sufiyan ne kaha : jaisey ( shahanshaah ( hai. aur Ahmad-bin-Hanbal ne kaha : maine abu Amr ( Ishaq-bin-muraar Shebani , nahwi , koofi) se akhna' ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : (iske mana hain) auza' (intihai haqeer)."
5672,"hamein Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se khabar di, kaha : ye hadisein hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye hadis ( bhi) hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ke nazdeek qiyamat ke din sabse zyada gandaa aur ghazab ka mustahiq shakhs wo hoga jo shahnshaah kahlata hoga, Allah ke siwa koi aur badshah nahi hai."
5673,"hamein Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se khabar di, kaha : ye hadisein hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye hadis ( bhi) hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ke nazdeek qiyamat ke din sabse zyada gandaa aur ghazab ka mustahiq shakhs wo hoga jo shahnshaah kahlata hoga, Allah ke siwa koi aur badshah nahi hai."
5674,"Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Abdullah-bin-Ubai Talha (Raziallahu anhu) paida huey to main unhein lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik dhaarii daar abaa (chadar) pahney apne aik oont ko) khaarish se nijat dilaane ke liye) gandhak (ya taarkol) laga rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kuchh khajoor sath hai? maine kaha : ji haan , phir maine aapko kuchh khajoorein pesh kin, aap ne unko apne munh mein daala , unhein chabaya , phir bachchey ka munh khol kar unko apne munh mubarak se seedhey-seedhey uske munh mein daal diya. bachchey ne zaban hilaa kar uska zaayqa lena shuru kar diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye Ansar ki khajooron se mohabbat hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska naam Abdullah rakha."
5675,"Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Abdullah-bin-Ubai Talha (Raziallahu anhu) paida huey to main unhein lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik dhaarii daar abaa (chadar) pahney apne aik oont ko) khaarish se nijat dilaane ke liye) gandhak (ya taarkol) laga rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kuchh khajoor sath hai? maine kaha : ji haan , phir maine aapko kuchh khajoorein pesh kin, aap ne unko apne munh mein daala , unhein chabaya , phir bachchey ka munh khol kar unko apne munh mubarak se seedhey-seedhey uske munh mein daal diya. bachchey ne zaban hilaa kar uska zaayqa lena shuru kar diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye Ansar ki khajooron se mohabbat hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska naam Abdullah rakha."
5676,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : hamein Ibne-Aun ne Ibne-Sirin se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ladka bimar tha, wo bahar gaey huey they ke wo ladka faut ho gaya. jab wo lot kar aaey to unhon-ne puchha ke mera bachcha kaisa hai? (unki biwi ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab pahley ki nisbat usko aaraam hai (ye maut ki taraf ishara hai aur kuchh jhoot bhi nahi) . phir Umme-Sulaim Sham ka khana unke paas laaein to unhon-ne khaaya. iske baad Umme-Sulaim se sohbat ki. jab farigh huey to Umme-Sulaim ne kaha ke jao bachche ko dafn kar do. phir subah ko abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sab haal bayan kiya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kya tum ne raat ko apni biwi se sohbat ki thi? abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki ke aey Allah in donon ko barkat de. phir Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan ladka paida hua to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha ke us bachchey ko utha kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley ja aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne bachchey ke sath thodi khajoorein bhi bhejin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bachchey ko ley liya aur puchha ke iske sath kuchh hai? logon ne kaha ke khajoorein hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajooron ko lekar chabaya, phir apne munh se nikal kar bachchey ke munh mein daal kar usey ghutthi di aur iska naam Abdullah rakha."
5677,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : hamein Ibne-Aun ne Ibne-Sirin se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ladka bimar tha, wo bahar gaey huey they ke wo ladka faut ho gaya. jab wo lot kar aaey to unhon-ne puchha ke mera bachcha kaisa hai? (unki biwi ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab pahley ki nisbat usko aaraam hai (ye maut ki taraf ishara hai aur kuchh jhoot bhi nahi) . phir Umme-Sulaim Sham ka khana unke paas laaein to unhon-ne khaaya. iske baad Umme-Sulaim se sohbat ki. jab farigh huey to Umme-Sulaim ne kaha ke jao bachche ko dafn kar do. phir subah ko abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sab haal bayan kiya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kya tum ne raat ko apni biwi se sohbat ki thi? abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki ke aey Allah in donon ko barkat de. phir Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan ladka paida hua to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha ke us bachchey ko utha kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley ja aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne bachchey ke sath thodi khajoorein bhi bhejin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bachchey ko ley liya aur puchha ke iske sath kuchh hai? logon ne kaha ke khajoorein hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajooron ko lekar chabaya, phir apne munh se nikal kar bachchey ke munh mein daal kar usey ghutthi di aur iska naam Abdullah rakha."
5678,"Hammad-bin-Mas-ada ne kaha : hamein Ibne-Aun ne Muhammad ( Ibne-Sirin ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se usi qissey ke sath Yazeed ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
5679,"Hammad-bin-Mas-ada ne kaha : hamein Ibne-Aun ne Muhammad ( Ibne-Sirin ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se usi qissey ke sath Yazeed ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
5680,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : mere yahan aik ladka paida hua, mein usko lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, aap ne iska naam Ibrahim rakha aur usko aik khajoor (ke daney) se ghutti di."
5681,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : mere yahan aik ladka paida hua, mein usko lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, aap ne iska naam Ibrahim rakha aur usko aik khajoor (ke daney) se ghutti di."
5682,"Shuaib-bin-Ishaq ne kaha : mujhey Hisham-bin-Urwa ne bataya , kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair aur Fatima-binte-munzir-bin-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : ke Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) (Makka se) hijrat ki niyat se jis waqt niklin , unke pet mein Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) they (yani haamla thin) jab wo Quba mein aa kar utrein to wahan saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) paida huey. phir wilaadat ke baad unhein lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein taake Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko ghutti lagaaein, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) se ley liya aur apni god mein bithaya , phir aik khajoor mangwaai. Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke ham aik ghadi tak khajoor dhoondtey rahe, aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ko chabaayaa, phir (iska joos) unke munh mein daal diya. yahi pehli cheez jo Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke pet mein pahunchi , wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka thook tha. Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke uske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) par hath phera aur unke liye dua ki aur unka naam Abdullah rakha. phir jab wo saat (7) ya aath (8) baras ke huey to saiyedna Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke ishaarey par wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ke liye aaey. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko aatey dekha to tabassum farmaya, phir unse (barkat ke liye) bait ki (kyonke wo kam-sin they)."
5683,"Shuaib-bin-Ishaq ne kaha : mujhey Hisham-bin-Urwa ne bataya , kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair aur Fatima-binte-munzir-bin-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : ke Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) (Makka se) hijrat ki niyat se jis waqt niklin , unke pet mein Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) they (yani haamla thin) jab wo Quba mein aa kar utrein to wahan saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) paida huey. phir wilaadat ke baad unhein lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein taake Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko ghutti lagaaein, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) se ley liya aur apni god mein bithaya , phir aik khajoor mangwaai. Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke ham aik ghadi tak khajoor dhoondtey rahe, aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ko chabaayaa, phir (iska joos) unke munh mein daal diya. yahi pehli cheez jo Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke pet mein pahunchi , wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka thook tha. Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke uske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) par hath phera aur unke liye dua ki aur unka naam Abdullah rakha. phir jab wo saat (7) ya aath (8) baras ke huey to saiyedna Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke ishaarey par wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ke liye aaey. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko aatey dekha to tabassum farmaya, phir unse (barkat ke liye) bait ki (kyonke wo kam-sin they)."
5684,"abu-Usama ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke wo Makka mein haamla huin, Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) unke pet mein they, Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke jab main (Makka se) nikli to main poorey dinon se thi, phir main Madina aai aur Quba mein thahri aur Quba mein maine usey ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) ko janm diya. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to aap ne usey apni god mein ley liya, phir aap ne khajoor mangwaai , usey chabaayaa . phir apna luaab dahan iske munh mein daal diya, pehli cheez jo iske pet mein gaee wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka lua'ab dahan tha. phir aap ne ( chabaai hui ( khajoor ki ghutti iske taaloo ko lagai, phir uske liye dua ki, barkat mangi , ( hijrat Madina ke baad) ye pahlaa bachcha tha jo Islam mein paida hua."
5685,"abu-Usama ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke wo Makka mein haamla huin, Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) unke pet mein they, Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke jab main (Makka se) nikli to main poorey dinon se thi, phir main Madina aai aur Quba mein thahri aur Quba mein maine usey ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) ko janm diya. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to aap ne usey apni god mein ley liya, phir aap ne khajoor mangwaai , usey chabaayaa . phir apna luaab dahan iske munh mein daal diya, pehli cheez jo iske pet mein gaee wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka lua'ab dahan tha. phir aap ne ( chabaai hui ( khajoor ki ghutti iske taaloo ko lagai, phir uske liye dua ki, barkat mangi , ( hijrat Madina ke baad) ye pahlaa bachcha tha jo Islam mein paida hua."
5686,"Ali-bin-Mus'hir ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf hijrat ki, us waqt wo Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se haamla thin, phir abu-Usama ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
5687,"Ali-bin-Mus'hir ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf hijrat ki, us waqt wo Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se haamla thin, phir abu-Usama ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
5688,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bachchey laey jatey, aap unke liye barkat ki dua kartey aur unhein ghutti detey."
5689,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bachchey laey jatey, aap unke liye barkat ki dua kartey aur unhein ghutti detey."
5690,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, kaha : ham ghutti dilwaaney ke liye Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein le gaey, ham ne khajoor hasil karni chahi to hamarey liye uska husool dushwar ho gaya."
5691,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, kaha : ham ghutti dilwaaney ke liye Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein le gaey, ham ne khajoor hasil karni chahi to hamarey liye uska husool dushwar ho gaya."
5692,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai, kaha : ke abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ka beta munzir , jab paida hua to usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko apni raan par rakha aur (iske walid ( abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) baithey they phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi cheez mein apne samney mutwajjeh huey to abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne hukm diya to wo bachcha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan par se utha liya gaya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khayal aaya to farmaya ke bachcha kahan hai? saiyedna abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! ham ne usko utha liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uska naam kya hai? abu-Usaid ne kaha ke falan naam hai, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, uska naam munzir hai. phir us din se unhon-ne iska naam munzir hi rakh diya."
5693,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai, kaha : ke abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ka beta munzir , jab paida hua to usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko apni raan par rakha aur (iske walid ( abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) baithey they phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi cheez mein apne samney mutwajjeh huey to abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne hukm diya to wo bachcha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan par se utha liya gaya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khayal aaya to farmaya ke bachcha kahan hai? saiyedna abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! ham ne usko utha liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uska naam kya hai? abu-Usaid ne kaha ke falan naam hai, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, uska naam munzir hai. phir us din se unhon-ne iska naam munzir hi rakh diya."
5694,"Abu-Tayyah ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon se badh kar khush akhalaq they, mera aik bhai tha jisey abu-Umair kaha jata tha. (abu-Tayyaah ne) kaha : mera khayal hai) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha tha : uska doodh chhudaya ja chuka tha, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif latey aur usey dekhtey to farmatey : abu-Umair ! ( nughair ( ne kya kiya? wo bachcha us (parindey) se khelaa karta tha."
5695,"Abu-Tayyah ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon se badh kar khush akhalaq they, mera aik bhai tha jisey abu-Umair kaha jata tha. (abu-Tayyaah ne) kaha : mera khayal hai) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha tha : uska doodh chhudaya ja chuka tha, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif latey aur usey dekhtey to farmatey : abu-Umair ! ( nughair ( ne kya kiya? wo bachcha us (parindey) se khelaa karta tha."
5696,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : aey mere betey !
5697,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : aey mere betey !
5698,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid se, unhon-ne Qais-bin-abi-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se dajjal ke mutaalliq jitney sawalat maine kiye utney kisi aur ne nahi kiye, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : mere betey ! tumhen us ( dajjal ( se kya baat pareshan kar rahi hai? tumhen us se hargiz koi nuqsan na pahunchega. kaha : maine kaha : log samajhtey hain ke uske sath pani ki nehrein aur roti ke pahaad hongey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo Allah Taala ke nazdeek uski nisbat zyada zaleel hai."
5699,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid se, unhon-ne Qais-bin-abi-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se dajjal ke mutaalliq jitney sawalat maine kiye utney kisi aur ne nahi kiye, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : mere betey ! tumhen us ( dajjal ( se kya baat pareshan kar rahi hai? tumhen us se hargiz koi nuqsan na pahunchega. kaha : maine kaha : log samajhtey hain ke uske sath pani ki nehrein aur roti ke pahaad hongey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo Allah Taala ke nazdeek uski nisbat zyada zaleel hai."
5700,"Wakee , Hushaim , Jarir aur abu-Usama sab ne Ismail se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, unmein se tanha Yazeed ki hadis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye aey mere betey ke alfaz hain aur kisi ki hadis mein nahi hain."
5701,"Wakee , Hushaim , Jarir aur abu-Usama sab ne Ismail se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, unmein se tanha Yazeed ki hadis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye aey mere betey ke alfaz hain aur kisi ki hadis mein nahi hain."
5702,"Amr-bin-Muhammad-bin Bukair Naqid ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamein Yazeed-bin-khaseefa ne Basar-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : main Madina Munawra mein Ansar ki majlis mein betha hua tha itney mein abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) darey sahmey huey aaey, ham ne unse puchha aapko kya hua? unhon-ne bataya ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne meri taraf paigham bheja hai ke main unke paas aaoon. main unke darwazey par gaya aur teen martaba salam kiya unhon-ne mujhey salam ka jawab nahi diya to main lot aaya, unhon-ne kaha : aapko hamarey paas aaney se kis baat ne rokaa? maine kaha : main aaya tha, aap ke darwazey par khadey teen baar salam kiya, aap logon ne mujhey jawab nahi diya, isliye main lot gaya kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jab tum mein se koi shakhs teen baar ijazat maangey aur usey ijazat na di jaey to wo lot jaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : is par gawahi pesh karo warna main tum ko saza doonga. Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unke sath sirf wo shakhs ja kar khada hoga jo qaum mein se sabse kam Umr hai, Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine kaha ke main sabse kam Umr hun to unhon-ne kaha : tum unke sath jao (aur gawahi do)."
5703,"Amr-bin-Muhammad-bin Bukair Naqid ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamein Yazeed-bin-khaseefa ne Basar-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : main Madina Munawra mein Ansar ki majlis mein betha hua tha itney mein abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) darey sahmey huey aaey, ham ne unse puchha aapko kya hua? unhon-ne bataya ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne meri taraf paigham bheja hai ke main unke paas aaoon. main unke darwazey par gaya aur teen martaba salam kiya unhon-ne mujhey salam ka jawab nahi diya to main lot aaya, unhon-ne kaha : aapko hamarey paas aaney se kis baat ne rokaa? maine kaha : main aaya tha, aap ke darwazey par khadey teen baar salam kiya, aap logon ne mujhey jawab nahi diya, isliye main lot gaya kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jab tum mein se koi shakhs teen baar ijazat maangey aur usey ijazat na di jaey to wo lot jaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : is par gawahi pesh karo warna main tum ko saza doonga. Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unke sath sirf wo shakhs ja kar khada hoga jo qaum mein se sabse kam Umr hai, Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine kaha ke main sabse kam Umr hun to unhon-ne kaha : tum unke sath jao (aur gawahi do)."
5704,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Yazeed-bin-khaseefa se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur ibne-abi-Umar ne apni hadis mein ye izafa kiya : Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main unke sath uth khada hua, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur gawahi di."
5705,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Yazeed-bin-khaseefa se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur ibne-abi-Umar ne apni hadis mein ye izafa kiya : Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main unke sath uth khada hua, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur gawahi di."
5706,"Bukair-bin-Ashajj se riwayat hai ke Basar-bin-Saeed ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : aik majlis mein ham Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas baithey huey they. itney mein Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ghussey ki haalat mein aaey aur khadey ho gaey phir kehney lagey : main tum ko Allah ki qism deta hun ke tum mein se kisi shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : ijazat teen baar mangi jati hai, agar tumhen ijazat mil jaey (to andar aa jaao), nahi to lot jao? Hazrat abi ne kaha mamla kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : maine kal Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas teen baar ijazat mangi, mujhey ijazat nahi di gaee to main lot gaya phir main aaj unke paas aaya to unke paas hazir ho gaya. maine unhein bataya ke main kal aaya tha, teen baar salam kya tha, phir chala gaya tha. kehney lagey ham ne sun liya tha, us waqt ham kisi kaam mein lagey huey they tum kyon na ijazat maangtey rahe yahan tak ke tumhen ijazat mil jati. maine kaha : maine isi tarah ijazat mangi jis tarah maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna tha. kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! main tumhari pusht aur peeth par kode maarunga phir tum koi aisa shakhs ley aao jo tumharey liye is par gawahi de. Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! tumharey sath ham mein se sirf wo khada hoga jo umr mein sabse chhota hai (badey to badey hain ye hadis ham mein se kam Umr logon ne bhi suni hai aur yad rakhi hai.) abu-Saeed ! utho, (unhon-ne kaha) to main utha , Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is tarah farmatey huey suna tha."
5707,"Bukair-bin-Ashajj se riwayat hai ke Basar-bin-Saeed ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : aik majlis mein ham Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas baithey huey they. itney mein Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ghussey ki haalat mein aaey aur khadey ho gaey phir kehney lagey : main tum ko Allah ki qism deta hun ke tum mein se kisi shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : ijazat teen baar mangi jati hai, agar tumhen ijazat mil jaey (to andar aa jaao), nahi to lot jao? Hazrat abi ne kaha mamla kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : maine kal Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas teen baar ijazat mangi, mujhey ijazat nahi di gaee to main lot gaya phir main aaj unke paas aaya to unke paas hazir ho gaya. maine unhein bataya ke main kal aaya tha, teen baar salam kya tha, phir chala gaya tha. kehney lagey ham ne sun liya tha, us waqt ham kisi kaam mein lagey huey they tum kyon na ijazat maangtey rahe yahan tak ke tumhen ijazat mil jati. maine kaha : maine isi tarah ijazat mangi jis tarah maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna tha. kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! main tumhari pusht aur peeth par kode maarunga phir tum koi aisa shakhs ley aao jo tumharey liye is par gawahi de. Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! tumharey sath ham mein se sirf wo khada hoga jo umr mein sabse chhota hai (badey to badey hain ye hadis ham mein se kam Umr logon ne bhi suni hai aur yad rakhi hai.) abu-Saeed ! utho, (unhon-ne kaha) to main utha , Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is tarah farmatey huey suna tha."
5708,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : hamein Saeed bin Yazeed ne abu-Nazara se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke darwazey par gaey aur ijazat talab ki, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye aik baar hai. phir unhon-ne dobara ijazat talab ki, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye dusri baar hai. phir unhon-ne teesri baar ijazat talab ki, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye teesri baar hai, phir wo lot gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( agley din) kisi ko unke peechhey rawaana kya aur unhein dobara bula bheja. phir (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) unse kaha : agar ye aisi baat hai jo tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (sun kar) yad rakhi hai to theek hai, agar nahi to main tumhen (doosron ke liye nishan) ibrat bana doonga. Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to wo hamarey yahaan aaey aur kehney lagey : tumhen ilm nahi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ijazat teen baar talab ki jati hai? kaha : to log hansney lagey, kaha : maine (logon se kaha :) tumharey paas tumhara musalman bhai dara hua aaya hai aur tum hans rahe ho? (phir Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ( chalein main us saza mein aap ka hissedaar banunga phir wo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha : ye abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) hain (ye mere gawah hain.)"
5709,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : hamein Saeed bin Yazeed ne abu-Nazara se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke darwazey par gaey aur ijazat talab ki, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye aik baar hai. phir unhon-ne dobara ijazat talab ki, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye dusri baar hai. phir unhon-ne teesri baar ijazat talab ki, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye teesri baar hai, phir wo lot gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( agley din) kisi ko unke peechhey rawaana kya aur unhein dobara bula bheja. phir (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) unse kaha : agar ye aisi baat hai jo tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (sun kar) yad rakhi hai to theek hai, agar nahi to main tumhen (doosron ke liye nishan) ibrat bana doonga. Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to wo hamarey yahaan aaey aur kehney lagey : tumhen ilm nahi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ijazat teen baar talab ki jati hai? kaha : to log hansney lagey, kaha : maine (logon se kaha :) tumharey paas tumhara musalman bhai dara hua aaya hai aur tum hans rahe ho? (phir Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ( chalein main us saza mein aap ka hissedaar banunga phir wo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha : ye abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) hain (ye mere gawah hain.)"
5710,"Shoba ne abu-Salma Jurairi aur Saeed bin Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, Jurairi aur Saeed bin Yazeed donon ne abu-Nazara se riwayat ki, donon ne kaha : ham ne unhein Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se usi hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan kartey huey suna, jis tarah Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki hai."
5711,"Shoba ne abu-Salma Jurairi aur Saeed bin Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, Jurairi aur Saeed bin Yazeed donon ne abu-Nazara se riwayat ki, donon ne kaha : ham ne unhein Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se usi hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan kartey huey suna, jis tarah Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki hai."
5712,"Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki kaha : hamein Ata ne Ubaid-bin-Umair se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se teen martaba ijazat talab ki to jaisey unhon-ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko mashghool samjha aur wapas ho gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya ham ne Abdullah-bin-Qais ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu)) ki awaz nahi suni thi? unko andar aaney ki ijazat do, (Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) wapas chaley gaey huey they, doosrey din) Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya gaya Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum ne aisa kyon kiya? unhon-ne kaha : hamein yahi ( karne ka ( hukm diya jata tha. unhon-ne kaha : tum is par gawahi dilao , nahi to main (wo ( karunga (jo karunga ( wo (Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu)) nikley Ansar ki majlis mein aaey unhon-ne kaha : is baat par tumharey haq main aur koi nahi, ham mein se jo sabse chhota hai wahi gawahi dega. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney ( khadey ho kar kaha : hamein ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein) usi ka hukm diya jata tha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye hukm mujh se ojhal reh gaya, bazaron mein hone-waale sodon ne mujhey us se mashghool kar diya."
