5715,abu-Aasim aur Nazar-bin-Shumail donon ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki. aur nazar ki hadis mein unhon-ne bazaron mein hone-waale sodon ne mujhey us se mashghool kar diya ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye.
5716,"Fazal bin-Musa ne kaha : hamein Talha bin Yahya ne abu-Burda se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha : Assalaamualaikum , Abdullah-bin-Qais ( hazir hua) hai, unhon-ne aaney ki ijazat na di. unhon-ne phir kaha : Assalaamualaikum , ye abu-Musa hai, Assalaamualaikum , ye Ash-ari hai, iske baad chaley gaey, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unko mere paas wapas laao. mere paas wapas laao. wo aaey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : abu-Musa ! aapko kis baat ne lota diya ? ham kaam mein mashghool they. unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : ijazat teen baar talab ki jaey, agar tum ko ijazat de di jaey (to aa jaao) warna lot jao. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya to aap is par gawah laaengey ya phir main ye karunga to Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) chaley gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha abu-Musa ko gawah mil gaya to Sham ko wo tumhen member ke paas milengey aur agar unko gawah nahi mila to wo tumhen nahi milengey, jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Sham ko aaey to unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko maujood paya , unhon-ne kaha abu-Musa ! kya kehtey hain? aapko gawah mil gaya? unhon-ne kaha : haan! Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) hain unhon (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : wo qaabile-bharosa gawah hain. (phir abu Tufail Aamir bin Wasila (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar) kaha : abu Tufail! ye (Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) kya kehtey hain? unhon (Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : ibne-khattaab ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap yahi farma rahe they. lihaza aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) par azab na banein. unhon-ne kaha : Subhan-Allah! maine aik cheez suni aur chaha ke uska saboot hasil karun."
5717,"Fazal bin-Musa ne kaha : hamein Talha bin Yahya ne abu-Burda se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha : Assalaamualaikum , Abdullah-bin-Qais ( hazir hua) hai, unhon-ne aaney ki ijazat na di. unhon-ne phir kaha : Assalaamualaikum , ye abu-Musa hai, Assalaamualaikum , ye Ash-ari hai, iske baad chaley gaey, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unko mere paas wapas laao. mere paas wapas laao. wo aaey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : abu-Musa ! aapko kis baat ne lota diya ? ham kaam mein mashghool they. unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : ijazat teen baar talab ki jaey, agar tum ko ijazat de di jaey (to aa jaao) warna lot jao. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya to aap is par gawah laaengey ya phir main ye karunga to Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) chaley gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha abu-Musa ko gawah mil gaya to Sham ko wo tumhen member ke paas milengey aur agar unko gawah nahi mila to wo tumhen nahi milengey, jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Sham ko aaey to unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko maujood paya , unhon-ne kaha abu-Musa ! kya kehtey hain? aapko gawah mil gaya? unhon-ne kaha : haan! Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) hain unhon (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : wo qaabile-bharosa gawah hain. (phir abu Tufail Aamir bin Wasila (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar) kaha : abu Tufail! ye (Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) kya kehtey hain? unhon (Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : ibne-khattaab ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap yahi farma rahe they. lihaza aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) par azab na banein. unhon-ne kaha : Subhan-Allah! maine aik cheez suni aur chaha ke uska saboot hasil karun."
5718,"Ali-bin Hashim ne Talha bin Yahya se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : to unhon (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : abu munzir ! ( Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat ( kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis suni thi? unhon-ne kaha : haan, ibne-khattaab! to aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke liye azab na banein aur unhon-ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul : Subhan-Allah aur uske baad ka hissa zikr nahi kya."
5719,"Ali-bin Hashim ne Talha bin Yahya se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : to unhon (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : abu munzir ! ( Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat ( kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis suni thi? unhon-ne kaha : haan, ibne-khattaab! to aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke liye azab na banein aur unhon-ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul : Subhan-Allah aur uske baad ka hissa zikr nahi kya."
