5724,"Nazar-bin-Shumail abu-Aamir aqadi Wahab bin Jarir aur Bahaz, sab ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, un sab ki hadis mein (ye jumla bhi) hai : jaisey aap ne usko na-pasand farmaya ho."
5725,"Nazar-bin-Shumail abu-Aamir aqadi Wahab bin Jarir aur Bahaz, sab ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, un sab ki hadis mein (ye jumla bhi) hai : jaisey aap ne usko na-pasand farmaya ho."
5726,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darwazey ki jhiri mein andar jhanka, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (lakdi ya lohe ka lambi lambi kai nokon wala) baal durust karne ka aik aala tha jis se aap sar khujaa rahe they, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko dekha to farmaya : agar mujhey yaqeeni taur par pata chal jata ke tum mujhey dekh rahe ho to main usko tumhari aankhon mein ghusa deta, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ijazat leney ka tariqa aankh hi ki wjah se to rakha gaya hai. (ke aankh kisi ko khilwat ke aalim mein na dekh sakey.)"
5727,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darwazey ki jhiri mein andar jhanka, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (lakdi ya lohe ka lambi lambi kai nokon wala) baal durust karne ka aik aala tha jis se aap sar khujaa rahe they, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko dekha to farmaya : agar mujhey yaqeeni taur par pata chal jata ke tum mujhey dekh rahe ho to main usko tumhari aankhon mein ghusa deta, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ijazat leney ka tariqa aankh hi ki wjah se to rakha gaya hai. (ke aankh kisi ko khilwat ke aalim mein na dekh sakey.)"
5728,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Sahal-bin-Sad Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darwazey mein bin janey wali jhiri mein se jhanka, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baal durust karne wala lohey ka aik aala tha jis se aap sar ke baalon ko sanwaar rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : agar main jaan leta ke tum waqei mujhey dekh rahe ho to main usko tumhari aankhon mein chubho deta. Allah ne ijazat leney ka tariqa aankh hi ke liye to rakha hai."
