5732,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hujrey mein jhanka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chode phal ka aik teer ya kai teer lekar uthey jaisey main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh raha hun ke aap khamoshi se uski aankhon mein wo teer chubhone ke imkan ka jaaiza ley rahe they.
