5734,"Suhel ke walid Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jisne ijazat ke baghair logon ke ghar mein taank jhank ki, unhein ijazat hai ke wo uski aankh phod din."
