5744,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham makaanon ke samney ki khuli jaghon mein baithey baatein kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey aur hamarey paas khadey ho gaey. aap ne farmaya : tumhara raston ki khali jaghon par majlison se kya sarokaar ? raston ki majaalis se ijtinab karo. ham ne kaha : ham aisi baton ke liye baithey hain jin mein kisi qism ki koi qabahat nahi, ham aik doosrey se guftgu aur baat cheet ke liye baithey hain, aap ne farmaya : agar nahi (reh saktey) to un ( jaghon (ke haq ada karo (jo ye hain) : nigaahein neechi rakhna, salam ka jawab dena aur achi guftgu karna."
