5766,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Muslim se unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas yahood mein se kuchh log aaey, unhon-ne aa kar kaha : ( السام عليك ya أبا القاسم ) ( abul-Qaasim ! aap par maut ho ( kaha aap ne farmaya : ( وَ عَلَيكُم ( (tum logon par ho!) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : balke tum par maut bhi ho zillat bhi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ! zaban buri na karo. unhon ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : aap ne nahi suna, unhon-ne kya kaha tha? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhon-ne jo kaha tha maine unko lota diya, maine kaha : tum par ho."
5767,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Muslim se unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas yahood mein se kuchh log aaey, unhon-ne aa kar kaha : ( السام عليك ya أبا القاسم ) ( abul-Qaasim ! aap par maut ho ( kaha aap ne farmaya : ( وَ عَلَيكُم ( (tum logon par ho!) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : balke tum par maut bhi ho zillat bhi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ! zaban buri na karo. unhon ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : aap ne nahi suna, unhon-ne kya kaha tha? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhon-ne jo kaha tha maine unko lota diya, maine kaha : tum par ho."
5768,"Yala bin Ubaid ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein Aamash ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unki baat samajh li (unhon-ne salam ke bajaey saam ka lafz bola tha) aur unhein bura bhala kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha ! bas karo, Allah Taala burai aur usey apna leney ko pasand nahi farmata aur ye izafa kya to is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ( وَإِذَا جَاءُوكَ حَيَّوْكَ بِمَا لَمْ يُحَيِّكَ بِهِ اللَّهُ ( nazil farmai : aur jab wo aap ke paas aatey hain to aapko is tarah salam nahi kehtey jis tarah Allah aapko salam kehta hai. aayat ke aakhir tak (aur apne dilon mein kehtey hain jo kuchh ham kehtey hain Allah is par hamein azab kyon nahi deta ? unke liye dozakh kafi hai jis mein wo jalengey aur wo lot kar janey ka badtareen thikana hai.)"
5769,"Yala bin Ubaid ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein Aamash ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unki baat samajh li (unhon-ne salam ke bajaey saam ka lafz bola tha) aur unhein bura bhala kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha ! bas karo, Allah Taala burai aur usey apna leney ko pasand nahi farmata aur ye izafa kya to is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ( وَإِذَا جَاءُوكَ حَيَّوْكَ بِمَا لَمْ يُحَيِّكَ بِهِ اللَّهُ ( nazil farmai : aur jab wo aap ke paas aatey hain to aapko is tarah salam nahi kehtey jis tarah Allah aapko salam kehta hai. aayat ke aakhir tak (aur apne dilon mein kehtey hain jo kuchh ham kehtey hain Allah is par hamein azab kyon nahi deta ? unke liye dozakh kafi hai jis mein wo jalengey aur wo lot kar janey ka badtareen thikana hai.)"
5770,"abu-Zubair ne kaha : unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : yahood mein se kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya aur kaha ( السام عليك ya أبا القاسم ) (abul-Qaasim aap par maut ho !) is par aap ne farmaya : tum par ho. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehney lagein aur wo ghussey mein aa gaee thin. kya aap ne nahi suna, jo unhon-ne kaha hai? aap ne farmaya : kyon nahi ! maine suna hai aur maine unko jawab de diya hai aur unke khilaf hamari dua qaboo hoti hai aur hamarey khilaf unki dua qabool nahi hoti ."
5771,"abu-Zubair ne kaha : unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : yahood mein se kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya aur kaha ( السام عليك ya أبا القاسم ) (abul-Qaasim aap par maut ho !) is par aap ne farmaya : tum par ho. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehney lagein aur wo ghussey mein aa gaee thin. kya aap ne nahi suna, jo unhon-ne kaha hai? aap ne farmaya : kyon nahi ! maine suna hai aur maine unko jawab de diya hai aur unke khilaf hamari dua qaboo hoti hai aur hamarey khilaf unki dua qabool nahi hoti ."
5772,"Abdul-Azeez darawardi ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yahood nasara ko salam kehney mein shuruat na karo aur jab tum unmein se kisi ko rastey mein milo (to bajaey iske wo ye kaam karey) tum usey rastey ke tang hissey ki taraf janey par majbur kar do."
5773,"Abdul-Azeez darawardi ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yahood nasara ko salam kehney mein shuruat na karo aur jab tum unmein se kisi ko rastey mein milo (to bajaey iske wo ye kaam karey) tum usey rastey ke tang hissey ki taraf janey par majbur kar do."
5774,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne hadis bayan ki, un sab (Shoba Sufiyan aur Jareer) ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. Wakee ki hadis mein hai, jab tum yahood se milo. Shoba se ibne-Jafar ki riwayat ki hui hadis mein hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahle-kitab ke barey mein farmaya aur Jarir ki riwayat mein hai : jab tum un logon se milo, aur mushrikon mein se kisi aik (giroh) ka naam nahi liya."
5775,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne hadis bayan ki, un sab (Shoba Sufiyan aur Jareer) ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. Wakee ki hadis mein hai, jab tum yahood se milo. Shoba se ibne-Jafar ki riwayat ki hui hadis mein hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahle-kitab ke barey mein farmaya aur Jarir ki riwayat mein hai : jab tum un logon se milo, aur mushrikon mein se kisi aik (giroh) ka naam nahi liya."
