5777,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne Sayyar se khabar di, unhon-ne Sabit Bunani se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un ( Ansar (ke ladkon ke paas se guzrey to aap ne unko salam kya."
5778,"Ismail bin Salim ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne khabar di, kaha : hamein sayyar ne isi sanad ke sath khabar di."
5779,"Ismail bin Salim ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne khabar di, kaha : hamein sayyar ne isi sanad ke sath khabar di."
5780,"Shoba ne sayyar se riwayat ki, kaha : main Sabit Bunani ke sath ja raha tha wo kuchh bachchon ke paas se guzrey to unhein salam kya, phir Sabit ne ye hadis bayan ki ke wo Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ja rahe they wo bachchon ke paas se guzrey to unhon-ne unko salam kya aur Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ja rahe they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bachchon ke paas se guzrey to unko salam kya."
5781,"Shoba ne sayyar se riwayat ki, kaha : main Sabit Bunani ke sath ja raha tha wo kuchh bachchon ke paas se guzrey to unhein salam kya, phir Sabit ne ye hadis bayan ki ke wo Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ja rahe they wo bachchon ke paas se guzrey to unhon-ne unko salam kya aur Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ja rahe they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bachchon ke paas se guzrey to unko salam kya."
5782,"Abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne kaha : hamein Hasan-bin-Ubaidullah ne hadis bayan ki. kaha : hamein Ibrahim bin Suwed ne hadis sunai kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : tumharey liye mere paas aaney ki yahi ijazat hai ke hijaab utha diya jaey aur tum mere raaz ki baat sun lo, (ye ijazat us waqt tak hai) yahan tak ke main tumhen rok dun."
5783,"Abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne kaha : hamein Hasan-bin-Ubaidullah ne hadis bayan ki. kaha : hamein Ibrahim bin Suwed ne hadis sunai kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : tumharey liye mere paas aaney ki yahi ijazat hai ke hijaab utha diya jaey aur tum mere raaz ki baat sun lo, (ye ijazat us waqt tak hai) yahan tak ke main tumhen rok dun."
5784,Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Hasan-bin- Abdullah se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5785,Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Hasan-bin- Abdullah se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5786,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : parda ham par laagu ho janey ke baad Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye bahar niklin, Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) jasaamat mein badi thin, jismani taur par aurton se unchi ( nazar aati) thin. jo shakhs unhein janta ho (pardey ke bawajood) uske liye makhfi nahi rehti thin, Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein dekh kar kaha : Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ! Allah ki qism ! aap ham se posheeda nahi reh saktin isliye dekh lijiye aap kaisey bahar nikla karengi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) (ye suntey hi ( ultey paon lot aaein aur (us waqt) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan raat ka khana tanaawul farma rahe they. aap ke hath mein gosht wali aik haddi thi wo andar aaein aur kehney lagin. Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main bahar nikli thi aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey is-is tarah kaha. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : usi waqt Allah Taala ne aap par wahi nazil farmai, phir aap se wahi ki kaifiyat zaayel ho gaee, haddi isi tarah aap ke hath mein thi, aap ne usey rakha nahi tha, aap ne farmaya : tum sab (ummahaatul-momeneen) ko ijazat de di gaee hai ke tum zarurat ke liye bahar ja sakti ho Abu-Bakar (ibne-Abi-Sheba) ki riwayat mein hai : unka jism aurton se uncha tha Abu-Bakar ne apni hadis (ki sanad) mein ye izafa kya : to Hisham ne kaha : aap ka maqsud qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye janey se tha."
5787,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : parda ham par laagu ho janey ke baad Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye bahar niklin, Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) jasaamat mein badi thin, jismani taur par aurton se unchi ( nazar aati) thin. jo shakhs unhein janta ho (pardey ke bawajood) uske liye makhfi nahi rehti thin, Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein dekh kar kaha : Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ! Allah ki qism ! aap ham se posheeda nahi reh saktin isliye dekh lijiye aap kaisey bahar nikla karengi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) (ye suntey hi ( ultey paon lot aaein aur (us waqt) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan raat ka khana tanaawul farma rahe they. aap ke hath mein gosht wali aik haddi thi wo andar aaein aur kehney lagin. Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main bahar nikli thi aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey is-is tarah kaha. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : usi waqt Allah Taala ne aap par wahi nazil farmai, phir aap se wahi ki kaifiyat zaayel ho gaee, haddi isi tarah aap ke hath mein thi, aap ne usey rakha nahi tha, aap ne farmaya : tum sab (ummahaatul-momeneen) ko ijazat de di gaee hai ke tum zarurat ke liye bahar ja sakti ho Abu-Bakar (ibne-Abi-Sheba) ki riwayat mein hai : unka jism aurton se uncha tha Abu-Bakar ne apni hadis (ki sanad) mein ye izafa kya : to Hisham ne kaha : aap ka maqsud qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye janey se tha."
5788,ibne-Numair ne kaha : Hisham ne hamein isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : wo aisi khatun thin ke unka jism logon se uncha (nazar aata) tha. (ye bhi) kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ka khana tanaawul farma rahe they.
5789,ibne-Numair ne kaha : Hisham ne hamein isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : wo aisi khatun thin ke unka jism logon se uncha (nazar aata) tha. (ye bhi) kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ka khana tanaawul farma rahe they.
5790,Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath hamein hadis bayan ki.
