5792,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan jab raat ko qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye bahar nikaltiin to manasey ki taraf jati thin, wo door aik khuli , badi jagah hai. aur Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye arz kartey rahtey they ke aap apni beeviyon ko parda karaaein , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kisi hikmat ki bina par) aisa nahi kartey they, phir aik raat ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) isha ke waqt (qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye) bahar niklein, wo daraaz (lambi) qad khatun thin, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us hirs mein ke hijaab nazil ho jaey, pukar kar unse kaha : Sauda ! ham ne aapko pehchan liya hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : is par Allah Taala ne hijaab nazil farma diya."
