5796,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : suno ! koi shakhs kisi shadi shuda aurat ke paas raat ko na rahe, siwaey-iske ke iska khawind ho ya mehram (ghair shadi shuda aurat ke paas rehna aur zyada sakhti se mana hai.)"
5797,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : suno ! koi shakhs kisi shadi shuda aurat ke paas raat ko na rahe, siwaey-iske ke iska khawind ho ya mehram (ghair shadi shuda aurat ke paas rehna aur zyada sakhti se mana hai.)"
5798,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-Rumeh ne kaha : hamein Leis ne Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-al-khair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ( ajnabi) aurton ke yahan janey se bacho . Ansar mein se aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! dewar / jeth ke mutaalliq aap ka kya khayal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dewar / jeth to maut hai."
5799,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-Rumeh ne kaha : hamein Leis ne Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-al-khair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ( ajnabi) aurton ke yahan janey se bacho . Ansar mein se aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! dewar / jeth ke mutaalliq aap ka kya khayal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dewar / jeth to maut hai."
5800,"Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne Amr-bin-Haris , Lais-bin-Sad aur Hewa-bin-shureh wghaira se riwayat ki ke Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib ne unhein isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
5801,"Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne Amr-bin-Haris , Lais-bin-Sad aur Hewa-bin-shureh wghaira se riwayat ki ke Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib ne unhein isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
5802,"ibne-Wahab ne kaha : maine Lais-bin-Sad se suna, keh rahe they : hamov ( dewar / jeth ( khawind ka bhai hai. ya khawind ke rishte-daaron mein us jaisa rishta rakhney waalaa, maslan : iska chacha zaad wghaira ."
5803,"ibne-Wahab ne kaha : maine Lais-bin-Sad se suna, keh rahe they : hamov ( dewar / jeth ( khawind ka bhai hai. ya khawind ke rishte-daaron mein us jaisa rishta rakhney waalaa, maslan : iska chacha zaad wghaira ."
5804,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Juber ne kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis sunai ke banu-Hashim ke kuchh log Hazrat Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar gaey, phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aa gaey, Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) us waqt unke nikah mein thin. unhon-ne un logon ko dekha to unhein na-gawar guzra . unhon-ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batai , sath hi kaha : maine khair ke siwa kuchh nahi dekha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne (bhi) unhein (hazrat Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) ko) us se bari qarar diya hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par khadey huey aur farmaya : aaj ke baad koi shakhs kisi aisi aurat ke paas na jaey jiska khawind ghar par na ho, siwaey-iske ke uske sath aik ya do log hon."
5805,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Juber ne kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis sunai ke banu-Hashim ke kuchh log Hazrat Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar gaey, phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aa gaey, Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) us waqt unke nikah mein thin. unhon-ne un logon ko dekha to unhein na-gawar guzra . unhon-ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batai , sath hi kaha : maine khair ke siwa kuchh nahi dekha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne (bhi) unhein (hazrat Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) ko) us se bari qarar diya hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par khadey huey aur farmaya : aaj ke baad koi shakhs kisi aisi aurat ke paas na jaey jiska khawind ghar par na ho, siwaey-iske ke uske sath aik ya do log hon."
5806,"Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ghar se bahar) apni aik ahliya ke sath they, aap ke paas se aik shakhs guzra to aap ne usey bula liya , jab wo aaya to aap ne farmaya : aey falan ! ye meri falan biwi hai. us shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main kisi ke barey mein guman karta bhi to aap ke barey main to nahi kar sakta tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shaitan insan ki ragon mein khoon ki tarah daudta hai."
5807,"Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ghar se bahar) apni aik ahliya ke sath they, aap ke paas se aik shakhs guzra to aap ne usey bula liya , jab wo aaya to aap ne farmaya : aey falan ! ye meri falan biwi hai. us shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main kisi ke barey mein guman karta bhi to aap ke barey main to nahi kar sakta tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shaitan insan ki ragon mein khoon ki tarah daudta hai."
5808,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ali-bin-Husain se, unhon-ne Hazrat Safiya-binte-Huyi (Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Ummul-Momenin Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aetikaf mein they, mein raat ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ziyaarat ko aai. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baatein kin, phir main lot janey ko khadi hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi mujhey pahuncha dene ko mere sath khadey huey aur mera ghar Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke makan mein tha. raah mein Ansar ke do aadmi miley jab unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to wo jaldi-jaldii chalney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thehro, ye Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) hai. wo donon boley ke Subhan-Allah ya Rasulullah ! (yani ham bhala aap par koi bad-gumaani kar saktey hain?) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke shaitan insan ke badan mein khoon ki tarah phirtaa hai aur main dara ke kahin tumharey dil mein bura khayal na daley. (aur uski wjah se tum tabah ho)."
5809,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ali-bin-Husain se, unhon-ne Hazrat Safiya-binte-Huyi (Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Ummul-Momenin Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aetikaf mein they, mein raat ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ziyaarat ko aai. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baatein kin, phir main lot janey ko khadi hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi mujhey pahuncha dene ko mere sath khadey huey aur mera ghar Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke makan mein tha. raah mein Ansar ke do aadmi miley jab unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to wo jaldi-jaldii chalney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thehro, ye Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) hai. wo donon boley ke Subhan-Allah ya Rasulullah ! (yani ham bhala aap par koi bad-gumaani kar saktey hain?) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke shaitan insan ke badan mein khoon ki tarah phirtaa hai aur main dara ke kahin tumharey dil mein bura khayal na daley. (aur uski wjah se tum tabah ho)."
5810,"Shuaib ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Ali-bin-Husain ne bataya ke unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke wo Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aetikaf ke doran masjid mein aap se milney aaein. unhon-ne ghadi bhar aap se baat ki, phir waapsi ke liye khadi ho gain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi unko wapas chhodney ke liye khadey ho gaey. iske baad (Shuaib ne) Mamar ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shaitan insan ke andar wahan pahunchta hai jahan khoon pahunchta hai. unhon-ne daudta hua nahi kaha."
5811,"Shuaib ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Ali-bin-Husain ne bataya ke unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke wo Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aetikaf ke doran masjid mein aap se milney aaein. unhon-ne ghadi bhar aap se baat ki, phir waapsi ke liye khadi ho gain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi unko wapas chhodney ke liye khadey ho gaey. iske baad (Shuaib ne) Mamar ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shaitan insan ke andar wahan pahunchta hai jahan khoon pahunchta hai. unhon-ne daudta hua nahi kaha."
5812,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha se riwayat ki ke aqeel-bin-abi-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Murra ne unhein Hazrat abu-Waqid Lesi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein baithey they aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, itney mein teen aadmi aaey, do to seedhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur aik chala gaya. wo do jo aaey unmein se aik ne majlis mein jagah khali paai to wo wahan baith gaya aur doosra logon ke peechhey betha aur tesraa to peeth pher kar chal diya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farigh huey to farmaya kya main tum se teen aadmiyon ka haal na kahun? aik ne to Allah ke paas thikana liya to Allah ne usko jagah di aur doosrey ne (logon mein ghusney ki) sharm ki to Allah ne bhi us se sharm ki aur teesrey ne munh phera to Allah ne bhi us se munh pher liya."
