5818,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : koi shakhs kisi doosrey shakhs ko uski jagah se na uthaey ke phir wahan baith jaey, balke khuley ho kar baitho aur wusat paida karo."
5819,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : koi shakhs kisi doosrey shakhs ko uski jagah se na uthaey ke phir wahan baith jaey, balke khuley ho kar baitho aur wusat paida karo."
5820,"abu-Rabe aur abu-Kamil ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Ayub ne hadis sunai. Yahya-bin-Habib ne kaha : hamein Rooh ne hadis sunai, Muhammad-bin-Raafe ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Razzaq ne hadis bayan ki, un donon (Rooh aur Abdur-Razzaq) ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, Muhammad-bin-Raafe ne kaha : hamein ibne-abi-fidya ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Suhak-bin-Usman ne khabar di, un sab (Ayub ibne-Juraij aur Suhak-bin-Usman) ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Leis ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, unhon-ne us hadis mein : balke khuley ho kar baitho aur wusat paida karo ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye aur (ibne- Raafe ne) ibne-Juraij ki hadis mein ye izafa kiya : maine un (ibne-bin-Juraij) se puchha : Juma ke din? unhon-ne kaha : Juma mein aur uske ilawa bhi."
5821,"abu-Rabe aur abu-Kamil ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Ayub ne hadis sunai. Yahya-bin-Habib ne kaha : hamein Rooh ne hadis sunai, Muhammad-bin-Raafe ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Razzaq ne hadis bayan ki, un donon (Rooh aur Abdur-Razzaq) ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, Muhammad-bin-Raafe ne kaha : hamein ibne-abi-fidya ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Suhak-bin-Usman ne khabar di, un sab (Ayub ibne-Juraij aur Suhak-bin-Usman) ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Leis ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, unhon-ne us hadis mein : balke khuley ho kar baitho aur wusat paida karo ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye aur (ibne- Raafe ne) ibne-Juraij ki hadis mein ye izafa kiya : maine un (ibne-bin-Juraij) se puchha : Juma ke din? unhon-ne kaha : Juma mein aur uske ilawa bhi."
5822,"abdullah ne Mamar se, unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs apne bhai ko uski jagah se na uthaey ke phir uski jagah par baith jaey. (Saalim ne kaha) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye tareeq tha ke koi shakhs unke liye (khud bhi) apni jagah se uthta to wo uski jagah par na baithtey they."
