5828,"abu-Awana aur Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muhammad donon ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs khada ho aur abu-Awana ki hadis mein hai jab tum mein se koi shakhs apni jagah se khada ho. phir us jagah lot aaey to wahi us (jagah) ka zyada haqdaar hai."
5829,"abu-Awana aur Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muhammad donon ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs khada ho aur abu-Awana ki hadis mein hai jab tum mein se koi shakhs apni jagah se khada ho. phir us jagah lot aaey to wahi us (jagah) ka zyada haqdaar hai."
5830,Zenab binte-Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke aik mukhannas unke yahaan maujood tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi ghar par they wo Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke bhai se kehney laga : Abdullah-bin-Ubai Umayya ! agar kal (kalaan ko) Allah Taala tum logon ko Taaif par fateh ata farmaai to main tumhen Ghelaan ki beti ( baadiya-binte- Ghelaan (ka pata bataunga wo char silwaton ke sath samney aati hai (samney se jism par char silwatein padti hain) aur aath (8) silwaton ke sath peeth pher kar jati hai. (intihai farba jism ki hai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski ye baat sun li to aap ne farmaya : ye (mukhannas) tumharey yahaan dakhil na hua karein.
5831,Zenab binte-Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke aik mukhannas unke yahaan maujood tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi ghar par they wo Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke bhai se kehney laga : Abdullah-bin-Ubai Umayya ! agar kal (kalaan ko) Allah Taala tum logon ko Taaif par fateh ata farmaai to main tumhen Ghelaan ki beti ( baadiya-binte- Ghelaan (ka pata bataunga wo char silwaton ke sath samney aati hai (samney se jism par char silwatein padti hain) aur aath (8) silwaton ke sath peeth pher kar jati hai. (intihai farba jism ki hai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski ye baat sun li to aap ne farmaya : ye (mukhannas) tumharey yahaan dakhil na hua karein.
5832,"Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ke paas aik mukhannas aaya karta tha aur paak beeviyon (Raziallahu anhu) usey jinsi maamlaat se anjaan samjha karti thin. farmaya : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laye aur wo aap ki aik ahliya ke yahan betha hua aik aurat ki tareef kar raha tha wo kehney laga : jab wo aati hai to char silwaton ke sath aati hai aur jab peeth pherti hai to aath (8) silwaton ke sath peeth pherti hai. is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main dekh nahi raha ke jo kuchh yahan hai usey sab pata hai. ye log tumharey paas na aaya karein. to unhon ( ummehaatul-moominin (Raziallahu anhu)) ne us se parda kar liya."
5833,"Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ke paas aik mukhannas aaya karta tha aur paak beeviyon (Raziallahu anhu) usey jinsi maamlaat se anjaan samjha karti thin. farmaya : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laye aur wo aap ki aik ahliya ke yahan betha hua aik aurat ki tareef kar raha tha wo kehney laga : jab wo aati hai to char silwaton ke sath aati hai aur jab peeth pherti hai to aath (8) silwaton ke sath peeth pherti hai. is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main dekh nahi raha ke jo kuchh yahan hai usey sab pata hai. ye log tumharey paas na aaya karein. to unhon ( ummehaatul-moominin (Raziallahu anhu)) ne us se parda kar liya."
5834,"Hisham ke walid (Urwa) ne Hazrat Asma-binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne (hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha)) ne kaha : Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se nikah kiya to unke paas aik ghodey ke siwa na kuchh maal tha, na ghulam tha, na koi aur cheez thi. unke ghodey ko main hi chara dalti thi unki taraf se uski saari zimme-dari main sambhaalti. uski nigahdaasht (dekhbhaal) karti unke pani laney waley oont ke liye khajoor ki guthliyaan todti aur usey khilati main hi (us par) pani laati main hi unka pani ka dol seeti, aata goondhti, main achhi tarah roti nahi bana sakti thi to Ansar ki khawaateen mein se meri padaus mere liye roti bana detin, wo sachchi (dosti wali) auratein thin, unhon-ne ( Asma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko zamin ka jo tukda ata farmaya tha wahan se apne sar par guthliyaan rakh kar laati ye (zameen) taqriban do tehai farsakh (taqriban 3.35 km) ki masafat par thi. kaha : aik din main aa rahi thi guthliyaan mere sar par thin to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mili aap ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein se kuchh log aap ke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya, phir awaz se oont ko bitha ne lagey taake (guthliyon ka bojh darmyan mein rakhtey huey) mujhey apne peechhey bitha lein. unhon-ne (hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko mukhaatab kartey huey) kaha : mujhey sharm aai mujhey tumhari ghairat bhi malum thi to unhon (Zubair (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Allah janta hai ke tumhara apne sar par guthliyon ka bojh uthana Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sawar honey se zyada sakht hai. kaha : ( yahi kaifiyat rahi ( yahan tak ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mere paas ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ata karda , hadis : 5693 .) aik kaneez bhijwaa di aur us ne mujh se ghodey ki zimme-dari ley li. (mujhey aisa laga ( jaisey unhon-ne mujhey (ghulaami se) aazad kara diya hai."
5835,"Hisham ke walid (Urwa) ne Hazrat Asma-binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne (hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha)) ne kaha : Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se nikah kiya to unke paas aik ghodey ke siwa na kuchh maal tha, na ghulam tha, na koi aur cheez thi. unke ghodey ko main hi chara dalti thi unki taraf se uski saari zimme-dari main sambhaalti. uski nigahdaasht (dekhbhaal) karti unke pani laney waley oont ke liye khajoor ki guthliyaan todti aur usey khilati main hi (us par) pani laati main hi unka pani ka dol seeti, aata goondhti, main achhi tarah roti nahi bana sakti thi to Ansar ki khawaateen mein se meri padaus mere liye roti bana detin, wo sachchi (dosti wali) auratein thin, unhon-ne ( Asma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko zamin ka jo tukda ata farmaya tha wahan se apne sar par guthliyaan rakh kar laati ye (zameen) taqriban do tehai farsakh (taqriban 3.35 km) ki masafat par thi. kaha : aik din main aa rahi thi guthliyaan mere sar par thin to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mili aap ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein se kuchh log aap ke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya, phir awaz se oont ko bitha ne lagey taake (guthliyon ka bojh darmyan mein rakhtey huey) mujhey apne peechhey bitha lein. unhon-ne (hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko mukhaatab kartey huey) kaha : mujhey sharm aai mujhey tumhari ghairat bhi malum thi to unhon (Zubair (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Allah janta hai ke tumhara apne sar par guthliyon ka bojh uthana Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sawar honey se zyada sakht hai. kaha : ( yahi kaifiyat rahi ( yahan tak ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mere paas ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ata karda , hadis : 5693 .) aik kaneez bhijwaa di aur us ne mujh se ghodey ki zimme-dari ley li. (mujhey aisa laga ( jaisey unhon-ne mujhey (ghulaami se) aazad kara diya hai."
5836,"ibne-abi-Mulaika ne kaha ke Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke main ghar ki khidmaat sar anjam de kar Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat karti thi, unka aik ghoda tha, main uski dekh bhaal karti thi, mere liye ghar ki khidmaat mein se ghodey ki nigahdaasht (dekhbhal) se badh kar koi aur khidmat zyada sakht na thi. main uske liye chaara laati, uski har zarurat ka khayal rakhti aur uski nigahdaasht karti , kaha : phir unhein aik khaadima mil gaee, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh qaidi aaey to aap ne unke liye aik khaadima ata kar di. kaha is ne mujh se ghodey ki nigahdaasht (ki zimme-dari ( sanbhaal li aur mujh se bahut bada bojh hata liya. mere paas aik aadmi aaya aur kaha : umme-abdullaah ! main aik faqeer aadmi hun : mera dil chahta hai ke main aap ke ghar ke saaey mein (baith kar saudaa) bech liya karun. unhon-ne kaha : agar maine tumhen ijazat de di to Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) inkar kar dengey. jab Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) maujood hon to (us waqt) aa kar mujh se ijazat maangna, phir wo shakhs (hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki maujoodgi mein) aaya aur kaha : umme-abdullaah ! main aik faqeer aadmi hun aur chahta hun ke main aap ke ghar ke saaey mein (baith kar kuchh) bech liya karun unhon (Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne jawab diya : Madiney main tumharey liye mere ghar ke siwa aur koi ghar nahi hai? to Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : tumhen kya hua hai, aik faqeer aadmi ko saudaa bechney se rok rahi ho? wo bechney laga, yahan tak ke usne kafi kamaai kar li, maine wo khaadima usey bech di. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) andar aaey to us khaadima ki qeemat meri god mein padi thi, unhon-ne kaha, ye mujhey hiba kar do. to unhon-ne kaha : main isko sadqa kar chuki hun."
5837,"ibne-abi-Mulaika ne kaha ke Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke main ghar ki khidmaat sar anjam de kar Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat karti thi, unka aik ghoda tha, main uski dekh bhaal karti thi, mere liye ghar ki khidmaat mein se ghodey ki nigahdaasht (dekhbhal) se badh kar koi aur khidmat zyada sakht na thi. main uske liye chaara laati, uski har zarurat ka khayal rakhti aur uski nigahdaasht karti , kaha : phir unhein aik khaadima mil gaee, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh qaidi aaey to aap ne unke liye aik khaadima ata kar di. kaha is ne mujh se ghodey ki nigahdaasht (ki zimme-dari ( sanbhaal li aur mujh se bahut bada bojh hata liya. mere paas aik aadmi aaya aur kaha : umme-abdullaah ! main aik faqeer aadmi hun : mera dil chahta hai ke main aap ke ghar ke saaey mein (baith kar saudaa) bech liya karun. unhon-ne kaha : agar maine tumhen ijazat de di to Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) inkar kar dengey. jab Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) maujood hon to (us waqt) aa kar mujh se ijazat maangna, phir wo shakhs (hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki maujoodgi mein) aaya aur kaha : umme-abdullaah ! main aik faqeer aadmi hun aur chahta hun ke main aap ke ghar ke saaey mein (baith kar kuchh) bech liya karun unhon (Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne jawab diya : Madiney main tumharey liye mere ghar ke siwa aur koi ghar nahi hai? to Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : tumhen kya hua hai, aik faqeer aadmi ko saudaa bechney se rok rahi ho? wo bechney laga, yahan tak ke usne kafi kamaai kar li, maine wo khaadima usey bech di. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) andar aaey to us khaadima ki qeemat meri god mein padi thi, unhon-ne kaha, ye mujhey hiba kar do. to unhon-ne kaha : main isko sadqa kar chuki hun."
5838,"Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab teen shakhs (maujood) hon to aik ko chhod kar do aadmi aapas mein sargoshi na karein."
5839,"Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab teen shakhs (maujood) hon to aik ko chhod kar do aadmi aapas mein sargoshi na karein."
5840,"Ubaidullah, Lais-bin-Sad, Ayub (sakhtiyan) aur Ayub-bin-Musa un sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Malik ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki."
5841,"Ubaidullah, Lais-bin-Sad, Ayub (sakhtiyan) aur Ayub-bin-Musa un sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Malik ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki."
5842,"Mansoor ne abu-Waail (Shaqeeq) se, unhon-ne Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum teen log (eik saath) ho to aik ko chhod kar do aadmi aapasi sargoshi na karein. yahan tak ke tum bahut se logon mein mil jao, kahin aisa na ho ke ye (do ki sargoshi) usey ghamzada kar de."
5843,"Mansoor ne abu-Waail (Shaqeeq) se, unhon-ne Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum teen log (eik saath) ho to aik ko chhod kar do aadmi aapasi sargoshi na karein. yahan tak ke tum bahut se logon mein mil jao, kahin aisa na ho ke ye (do ki sargoshi) usey ghamzada kar de."
5844,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum teen log ho to apne sathi ko chhod kar do aapas mein sargoshi na karein kyonke ye cheez usko ghamzada kar degi."
5845,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum teen log ho to apne sathi ko chhod kar do aapas mein sargoshi na karein kyonke ye cheez usko ghamzada kar degi."
5846,Isa-bin-Yonus aur Sufiyan donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath (hadis bayan ki).
5847,Isa-bin-Yonus aur Sufiyan donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath (hadis bayan ki).
5848,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar hotey to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aapko dam kartey, wo kehtey : Allah ke naam se, wo aapko bachaaey aur har bimari se shifa de aur hasad karne waley ke shar se, jab wo hasad karey aur nazar lagaaney wali har aankh ke shar se. ( aapko mehfooz rakhey.)"
5849,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar hotey to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aapko dam kartey, wo kehtey : Allah ke naam se, wo aapko bachaaey aur har bimari se shifa de aur hasad karne waley ke shar se, jab wo hasad karey aur nazar lagaaney wali har aankh ke shar se. ( aapko mehfooz rakhey.)"
5850,"abu-Nazara ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! kya aap bimar ho gaey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan. Hazrat Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne ye kalimaat kahey : main Allah ke naam se aapko dam karta hun, har cheez se ( hifazat ke liye) jo aapko takleef de, har nafs aur har hasad karne wali aankh ke shar se, Allah aapko shifa de, mein Allah ke naam se aapko dam karta hun."
5851,"abu-Nazara ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! kya aap bimar ho gaey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan. Hazrat Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne ye kalimaat kahey : main Allah ke naam se aapko dam karta hun, har cheez se ( hifazat ke liye) jo aapko takleef de, har nafs aur har hasad karne wali aankh ke shar se, Allah aapko shifa de, mein Allah ke naam se aapko dam karta hun."
5852,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nazar haq (Sabit shuda baat) hai."
5853,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nazar haq (Sabit shuda baat) hai."
5854,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : nazar haq (Sabit shuda baat) hai, agar koi aisi cheez hoti jo taqdeer par sabqat ley ja sakti to nazar sabqat ley jati aur jab (nazare-bad ke ilaaj ke liye) tum se ghusl karne ke liye kaha jaey to ghusl kar lo."
5855,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : nazar haq (Sabit shuda baat) hai, agar koi aisi cheez hoti jo taqdeer par sabqat ley ja sakti to nazar sabqat ley jati aur jab (nazare-bad ke ilaaj ke liye) tum se ghusl karne ke liye kaha jaey to ghusl kar lo."
5856,"ibne-Numair ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par bani-zuraiq ke aik Yahudi Labeed-bin-A'sam ne jaadoo kiya. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khayal aata ke main ye kaam kar raha hun halanke wo kaam kartey na they. aik din ya aik raat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki, phir dua ki, phir farmaya ke aey Aaisha ! tujhey malum hua ke Allah jal jalaala ne mujhey wo batla diya jo maine us se poochha? . mere paas do aadmi aaey, aik mere sar ke paas betha aur doosra paon ke paas (wo donon Farishtey they) jo sar ke paas betha tha, us ne doosrey se kaha jo paon ke paas betha tha us ne sar ke paas baithey huey se kaha ke is shakhs ko kya bimari hai? wo bola ke is par jaadoo hua hai. usne kaha ke kis ne jaadoo kya hai? wo bola ke Labeed-bin-A'sam ne. phir usne kaha ke kis mein jaadoo kiya hai? wo bola ke kanghi mein aur un baalon mein jo kanghi se jhadey aur nar khajoor ke gaabhey ke reshey mein. usne kaha ke ye kahan rakha hai? wo bola ke zi-arwaan ke kunein mein. Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne chand ashaab ke sath us kunein par gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Aaisha ! Allah ki qism us kunein ka pani aisa tha jaisey mahndi ka zalaal (nichod) aur wahan ke khajoor ke darakht aisey they jaisey shaitanon ke sar . maine arz kiya ke ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko jalaa kyon nahi diya? (yani wo jo baal wghaira nikley) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey to Allah ne theek kar diya, ab mujhey logon mein fasad bhadkana bura malum hua, to maine hukm diya aur wo dafn kar diya gaya."
5857,"ibne-Numair ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par bani-zuraiq ke aik Yahudi Labeed-bin-A'sam ne jaadoo kiya. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khayal aata ke main ye kaam kar raha hun halanke wo kaam kartey na they. aik din ya aik raat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki, phir dua ki, phir farmaya ke aey Aaisha ! tujhey malum hua ke Allah jal jalaala ne mujhey wo batla diya jo maine us se poochha? . mere paas do aadmi aaey, aik mere sar ke paas betha aur doosra paon ke paas (wo donon Farishtey they) jo sar ke paas betha tha, us ne doosrey se kaha jo paon ke paas betha tha us ne sar ke paas baithey huey se kaha ke is shakhs ko kya bimari hai? wo bola ke is par jaadoo hua hai. usne kaha ke kis ne jaadoo kya hai? wo bola ke Labeed-bin-A'sam ne. phir usne kaha ke kis mein jaadoo kiya hai? wo bola ke kanghi mein aur un baalon mein jo kanghi se jhadey aur nar khajoor ke gaabhey ke reshey mein. usne kaha ke ye kahan rakha hai? wo bola ke zi-arwaan ke kunein mein. Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne chand ashaab ke sath us kunein par gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Aaisha ! Allah ki qism us kunein ka pani aisa tha jaisey mahndi ka zalaal (nichod) aur wahan ke khajoor ke darakht aisey they jaisey shaitanon ke sar . maine arz kiya ke ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko jalaa kyon nahi diya? (yani wo jo baal wghaira nikley) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey to Allah ne theek kar diya, ab mujhey logon mein fasad bhadkana bura malum hua, to maine hukm diya aur wo dafn kar diya gaya."
5858,"abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne hadis bayan ki, kaha, hamein Hisham ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaadoo kiya gaya. uskey baad abu-Kuraib ne waqiey ki tafseelaat samet ibne-Numair ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuwein ki taraf tashrif liye gaey, usey dekha, us kuwein par khajoor ke darakht they (jinhein kisi zamaney mein kuwein ke pani se sairaab kiya jata hoga) unhon (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)) ne kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! usey nikaalein (aur jalaa dein) abu-Kuraib ne : aap ne usey jalaa kyon na diya? ke alfaz nahi kahey aur ye alfaz (bhi) bayan nahi kiye : maine uske barey mein hukm diya to usko paat diya gaya."
5859,"abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne hadis bayan ki, kaha, hamein Hisham ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaadoo kiya gaya. uskey baad abu-Kuraib ne waqiey ki tafseelaat samet ibne-Numair ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuwein ki taraf tashrif liye gaey, usey dekha, us kuwein par khajoor ke darakht they (jinhein kisi zamaney mein kuwein ke pani se sairaab kiya jata hoga) unhon (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)) ne kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! usey nikaalein (aur jalaa dein) abu-Kuraib ne : aap ne usey jalaa kyon na diya? ke alfaz nahi kahey aur ye alfaz (bhi) bayan nahi kiye : maine uske barey mein hukm diya to usko paat diya gaya."
5860,"Khalid-bin-Haaris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hisham-bin-Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik Yahudi aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik zahar aalud (pakki hui) bakri lekar aai, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein se kuchh (gosht khaya) ( aapko iske zahar aalud honey ka pataa chal gaya) to us aurat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya gaya. aap ne us aurat se us (zahar) ke barey mein puchha to usne kaha : (naauzubillah !) main aapko qatl karna chahti thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala aisa nahi karega ke tumhen is baat par tasallut ( ikhtiyar ( de dey . unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( tumhen ( mujh par) tasallut de dey .) unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : kya ham usey qatl na kar dein ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi. unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : to main ab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh mubarak ke androoni hissey mein uskey asaraat ko pehchanta hun."
5861,"Khalid-bin-Haaris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hisham-bin-Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik Yahudi aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik zahar aalud (pakki hui) bakri lekar aai, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein se kuchh (gosht khaya) ( aapko iske zahar aalud honey ka pataa chal gaya) to us aurat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya gaya. aap ne us aurat se us (zahar) ke barey mein puchha to usne kaha : (naauzubillah !) main aapko qatl karna chahti thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala aisa nahi karega ke tumhen is baat par tasallut ( ikhtiyar ( de dey . unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( tumhen ( mujh par) tasallut de dey .) unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : kya ham usey qatl na kar dein ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi. unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : to main ab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh mubarak ke androoni hissey mein uskey asaraat ko pehchanta hun."
